nd building middlemarket manufacturing service and specialty consumer companies in the united states and canada the firms principals have historically achieved superior investment returns by employing a combination of strategic operating and financial experience to provide portfolio companies with competitive advantages gridirons principals work closely with management teams to develop strategies for portfolio companies as well as providing resources to execute business plans and build industryleading companies gridiron seeks control equity investments in manufacturing service and specialty consumer businesses with earnings before interest taxes depreciation and amortization ebitda of  million to  million moreless funding history datedeal sizeinvestors october th view dealapril th view dealcreate alertmanage your alerts in accountwant to know when gridiron capital fund iii lp gets fundedkey peoplethomas burger jrexecutive officereugene conese jrexecutive officerplease note that all data is automatically extracted and errors can occurthe whogotfunded team has not necessarily reviewed the information in this page and has not determined if it is accurate and completeinaccurate data help us improve whogotfunded post a comment gridiron capital wraps up third fund at  mln  pe hub subscribe to pe hub wire join over  of your peers get the mustread email for pevc professionals delivered to your inbox daily — for free us edition daily canada edition weekly we will not send you spam and we dont share your email address with rd parties i accept the terms and conditions subscribe yes no registersign in a community for professionals in private capital gridiron capital wraps up third fund at  mln october   by iris dorbian print email share via email separate multiple email addresses with commas share send me a copy email preview to from subject look at this story on pe hub gridiron capital wraps up third fund at  mln gridiron capital llc has closed its third fund at a hard cap of 